<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>대전광역시 - 시민을 행복하게 대전을 살맛나게</title>
</head>

<style>
.box{background:#fff; margin:130px auto 0; border-radius:10px; text-align:center; box-shadow: 3px 3px 1px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.03); border:1px solid #e6e6e6; padding:40px 55px; box-sizing:border-box; width:810px}
.box:after{content:''; display:block; height:1px; clear:both;}
.visual{position:relative; }
.visual:before{content:''; display:block; position:absolute; left:0; height:155px; width:185px; background:url(https://daejeon.go.kr/images/drh/layout/stop/pc_img.png); background-position:-30px -16px}
.visual:after{content:''; display:block; height:1px; clear:both;}
.visual .txt{padding-left:230px; text-align:left; height:155px}
.visual .txt strong{font-size:24px; letter-spacing:-1px; display:block; padding-top:10px}
.visual .txt p{color: #5c5c5c; line-height:22px; font-size:15px; padding-top:10px;}
.logo{text-align:center; padding-top:35px; clear:both; width:100%}

@media screen and (max-width:810px) {
	.box{width:90%; padding:30px 35px; margin:50px auto 0;}
}
@media screen and (max-width:730px) {
	.visual:before{display:none;}
	.visual .txt{height:auto; padding-left:0;}
}
</style>

<body style="background-color:#f8f8f8">
	<div class="box">
		<div class="visual">
			<div class="txt">
				<strong>웹페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다.</strong>
				<dl>
				<dt>가능성이 높은 원인:</dt>
				<dd>주소에 오타가 있을 수 있습니다.</dd>
				<dd>클릭한 링크가 만료 된 것일 수도 있습니다.</dd>
				</dl>
			</div>
		</div>	
	</div>
	<div class="logo"><img src="https://daejeon.go.kr/images/drh/layout/stop/logo.png" alt="대전광역시"/></div>
</body>
</html>
